augroup MyFormat
    autocmd!
    " C/C++
    autocmd InsertLeave *.c,*.cc,*.cpp,*.h,*.hpp undojoin|Neoformat! cpp
    autocmd FileType c,cpp nnoremap = :<C-u>Neoformat! cpp<CR>
    " Dlang
    autocmd InsertLeave *.d undojoin|Neoformat! d
    autocmd FileType d nnoremap = :<C-u>Neoformat! d<CR>
    " Python
    autocmd InsertLeave *.py undojoin|Neoformat! python
    autocmd FileType python nnoremap = :<C-u>Neoformat! python<CR>
augroup END
